OL,10,GVideo Games are commonly in English,
OL,11,GGerman, Japanese and many other
OL,12,Glanguages.. but what about less spoken
OL,13,Glanguages? Whilst I was working as the
OL,14,GLead Sound Designer on a AA game, I
OL,15,Galso ended up being the Welsh Language
OL,16,GLead on the project, with the help of
OL,17,Ga small team I chose the insane
OL,18,Gchallenge of translating a AA video
OL,19,Ggame into Welsh + Voice Acting with no
OL,20,Gprior experience in doing so and also
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
